# DS-0002: Dockerfile has no top-level USER directive.
# Intentional: supervisord must start as root so x11vnc/Xvfb can bind the
# display socket. The JVM is launched via `gosu app` inside supervisord.conf,
# so PlayGame runs as UID 1000 with no capabilities. Kyverno enforces
# no-privilege-escalation at the pod level.
AVD-DS-0002
